{
  "stem": "894.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it's against the very Orthodox rule to cut your beard, and so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was very intelligent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was very educated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People used to come to him-- he had magnificent handwriting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People used to come to them if they needed legal letters and such.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those are the things I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was a-- I was really very attached to my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think that my father was so immersed in his studies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was one of his great pleasures.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a brother who took after him that was really a giant scholar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I guess, me being the little one, and he having reached a certain age, didn't fuss around with me so much.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I don't remember any [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] cuddling with the father, you know, but which they probably didn't do-- the very Hasidic people, at any rate.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With my mother, I was very, very close.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I adored her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She used to get dressed Saturday morning to go to shul, and I would beg her to wake me up so that I can walk her.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I would turn around and come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was so proud of the way she looked, and so I would just take her around and walk with her.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember it was very beautifully conducted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father took a lot of time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you're supposed to explain to your children about the exodus from Egypt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And year after year, we would just sit there, and my father would say it in Hebrew, and then he would translate it in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this would go on and on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And since I don't remember my grandfather, and my grandmother always came for holidays and Saturdays.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And every day, actually, she came to visit.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
